<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yuàn tiān de de zhǔ jīn rì cì fú gěi nǐ 迦南1248</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yuàn tiān de de zhǔ zhì gāo de shén, jīn rì cì fú gěi nǐ.
 yīn wèi nǐ zūn xíng le fù de zhǐ yì, chū lí āi jí de.
 shén yào bǎ dí rén jiāo zài nǐ shǒu lǐ, tā yào bǎ féi wò de tǔ de cì gěi nǐ.
 tā bì qīn zì dài nǐ jìn rù yīng xǔ zhī de, shén de míng shì yīng dāng chēng sòng de.
 nǐ yào zòng héng zǒu biàn zhè de, chuán yáng tiān guó dà hǎo xìn xī.
 yǒng shēng de fú yīn zhǒng zi sā xià qù, dà de yī piàn shēng jī.
 yī dài yī dài qù chuán dì, zhǔ de fú yīn shēng shēng bù xī.
 shì jiè yīn fú yīn de dà néng ér gǎi biàn, zhǔ de míng zài quán de bèi gāo jǔ.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>1248</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>